		<span id="title-177903981" class="story-title"> <a   href="//hardware.slashdot.org/story/25/06/02/225250/texas-right-to-repair-bill-passes">Texas Right To Repair Bill Passes</a> <span class=" no extlnk"><a class="story-sourcelnk" href="https://www.theverge.com/law/678334/right-to-repair-texas-hb-2963"  title="External link - https://www.theverge.com/law/678334/right-to-repair-texas-hb-2963" target="_blank"> (theverge.com) </a></span></span>

		
		
